I wanted to share this experience at least once because i have been working on becoming more and more aware of things around me and our culture and heritage! 
I won’t call my self the most spiritual person but I’m getting there one step at a time, and i love the feeling of feeling absolutely nothing and yet everything at the same time! 
I’m finding my calm in the chaos of everyday life! 
And it’s a long road to heal to be better than yesterday, but i’ll get there! 
.
Also a special thanks to @nitikapanjwani_ because I absolutely love her aura and i love the fact that i get to learn so much about god/spirituality from her ✨
